instruction: Give a list of items that a person can take on a camping trip.
output:
- Tent 
- Sleeping bags 
- Flashlight 
- First-aid kit 
- Camping stove 
- Food 
- Matches 
- Cutlery and cookware 
- Firewood 
- Insect repellent 
- Water bottles 
- Sun protection 
- Clothes 
- Blanket 
- Map and compass 
- Emergency whistle 
- Binoculars
